title: New: Rochelle Jordan – Impossible
content:
Ending the year with a bang, Rochelle Jordan takes up this Lil Wayne beat and destroys it in the best way possible.

Whilst 2012 hasn’t quite been the year that RoJo exploded into the mainstream like I initially predicted, the hype has been slowly but surely building, putting her in a fantastic position heading into ’13. Mixing her soulful vocals and feisty flow with the near perfect production by KLSH, Impossible is may well be the last we hear of Jordan in 2012, but you can bet she’ll be back for more over the coming twelve months.
